.mt-10
  h2.headline Attempts today

  - if @attempts.empty?

    p No attempts today :'(

  - else

    table width="100%"

      - @attempts.each do |attempt|
        tr
          td
            b= attempt.word.name

          td= attempt.input

          td
            - if attempt.status == "success"
              span ‚úÖ
